Package: roostR
Title: Activity Pattern Analysis for Motus Radio-Telemetry Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kelly", "Williams", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "williak5@ohio.edu")
Description: Tools for detecting and quantifying nocturnal roosting behavior,
    roost timing, and restlessness in birds tagged with Motus radio transmitters.
    Converts raw signal-strength detections into behavioral metrics including
    roost onset time, roost departure time, observation coverage, and
    restlessness bout statistics.
